title: (Weds Early Bird) Bobby Can’t Believe What He Saw Outside His House This Morning + Lunchbox Reads Bobby’s New Book to His Kids + A BIG Thanks to the BTEAM
itunes:title: (Weds Early Bird) Bobby Can’t Believe What He Saw Outside His House This Morning + Lunchbox Reads Bobby’s New Book to His Kids + A BIG Thanks to the BTEAM
description:
Bobby couldn’t believe his eyes this morning of what he saw outside of his house. Lunchbox got his two son’s review of Bobby’s new book after reading it to him. We get an update from Navy Petty Officer 2nd Class Anthony Thompson, his wife Ivonne on the money you’ve been able to raise to rebuild his home!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
